6 AS INTRODUCED
7 An Act relating to schools; amending Section 1,
Chapter 297, O.S.L. 2024 (70 O.S. Supp. 2024, Section
8 6-401), which relates to student communication;
creating an opt-out exception; providing an effective
9 date; and declaring an emergency.
